skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: x. track tracking
des: xTrack is a Blockchain ready supply chain analytics and visibility tool, designed by SCT Software, that can be used to get real-time status of your shipments. You can tell me the carrier name with tracking number and I will provide you with the current status / location of your shipment... for example, you can say, Alexa, my carrier name is TNT and tracking number is 8 6 2 4 7 5 7 3 7.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
